Posts.Content: Wow! The drugs are sent from India???? Huge red flag.....please go to the website of these 'pharmacies' and check out their liability or lack thereof. As a Canadian, I know that if my drugs were sent via India/the pharmacy had NO liability for it's products, I'd not be using them. Please be very careful about the quality of your drugs, prescription or not. Jean
